 rankings, had never before been in the top tier of Washington lobbying firm=
s. According to PoliticalMoneyLine, which compiles a comprehensive annual li=
st of all lobbying firms, Greenberg Traurig had the 35th-highest income duri=
ng the first six months of last year.=20
